Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.89,0:00:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Episode 6{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.99,0:00:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You should leave now. I can go by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.02,0:00:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. Someone might kidnap you. It is dangerous at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.89,0:00:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.23,0:00:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But Mr. Priest, is it ok for you to go to church this late?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.40,0:00:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be going soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.01,0:00:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.18,0:00:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my in-law's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.72,0:00:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, Mi Young, you are the Queen's...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.66,0:00:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Timing and Subtitles brought to you by The Fated Team @ Viki{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.38,0:01:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You came.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.48,0:01:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.81,0:01:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, I've been wanting to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.55,0:01:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you that you wanted to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.39,0:01:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.26,0:01:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a neighborhood oppa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.20,0:01:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mi Young is like a sister I cherish.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.97,0:01:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,An oppa?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.20,0:01:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A neighborhood oppa?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.61,0:01:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that childish bandaid?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.98,0:01:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing. I got a small scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.51,0:01:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This happened when she was with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.05,0:01:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry. I should have protected her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.99,0:02:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to be sorry. It was all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.73,0:02:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.24,0:02:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.31,0:02:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.27,0:02:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Call me when something happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.38,0:02:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok. Thank you for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.67,0:02:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This is unbelievable. Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.04,0:02:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How long have you lived here that you have already made a friend in this neighborhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.55,0:02:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, he is a priest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.12,0:03:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I coincidentally met him, so we talked and he took me home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.52,0:03:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I give you some advice?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.99,0:03:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,While you live with me, live with class.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.76,0:03:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't hang out with a priest or punk, or whatever he is. Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.78,0:03:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Shameless man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.18,0:03:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is he to tell her to call him if something happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.81,0:03:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,She has a husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.87,0:03:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I... have something I want to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.51,0:03:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not in the mood to forgive anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.74,0:03:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not why I came, but
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.74,0:04:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I came because of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.49,0:04:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, are you saying that you will sign this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.33,0:04:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking about this all day,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.93,0:04:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I can give up the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I can raise the baby,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.27,0:04:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,loving it more than myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.74,0:04:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll prove it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.18,0:04:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.48,0:04:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you can feel
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.32,0:04:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,who the baby needs the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Signing this contract,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,can't you delay it for 10 months please?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.66,0:04:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask this of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.77,0:04:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.53,0:05:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,would be just wasting time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you sign it now or in 10 months, the fact that we will divorce will not change.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.98,0:05:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Mi Young, you are going to be the one giving up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,When that time comes, come here and sign this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.19,0:05:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That will be the only time you are allowed in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.89,0:05:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good. You understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good. Good. Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.01,0:05:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.08,0:05:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.92,0:05:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,since when did our Jangin Chemicals have a new tradition of pregnancy before marriage?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.15,0:05:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Our elders in the family are very angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.23,0:06:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.40,0:06:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have visited you first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.67,0:06:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.24,0:06:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a reason why this happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But still, there is a baby to continue the Lee family bloodline.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.04,0:06:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What is a greater happiness than this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.31,0:06:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.35,0:06:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The world is full of distrust.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying my grand-daughter-in-law
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.02,0:06:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,is pretending to be pregnant?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.02,0:06:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know where you heard that story, but
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don' t even wear fake branded socks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.86,0:06:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is the one spreading this kind of rumor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.54,0:06:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that your mother runs a restaurant by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.24,0:06:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm guessing it is a franchise restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.61,0:06:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.85,0:07:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a small anchovy rice wrap restaurant on Yeoul Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.45,0:07:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So, she isn't from the capital or a big city, but from some countryside island.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.99,0:07:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this unacceptable, elders?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.76,0:07:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The beach on Yeoul Island
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.47,0:07:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,has some of the cleanest water in our country.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.98,0:07:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And at night, you can see more stars than you have ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.71,0:07:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, the air is very, very fresh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.69,0:07:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Although it is small, it is a beautiful island.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.36,0:07:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.13,0:07:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm proud that Yeoul Island is my hometown.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.53,0:07:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a good girl as a daughter-in-law.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.14,0:07:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Gun wasn't so careful for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.31,0:08:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you find such an innocent girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.58,0:08:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Elders, these two have a complicated relationship...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.28,0:08:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,On my grand-daughter-in-law's island, there is a natural soap factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.29,0:08:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Our Gun took over that factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.96,0:08:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And through that, this couple met.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.96,0:08:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,How thankful is that soap?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The soap factory in Yeoul Island almost shutdown,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.70,0:08:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,but Gun promised to transfer it to Seoul.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So, all the Islanders are very thankful to Gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.39,0:08:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief Secretary Tak, what did they say they are going to build on Yeoul Island?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.96,0:08:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find out? What are they going to build?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.86,0:08:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You never told me to find that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.50,0:08:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this Chief Secretary Tak?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you only find things out when I tell you to?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.90,0:09:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Find it out quickly. Quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Se Ra{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.14,0:09:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time since I've heard your voice.{\b1} Were you busy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.58,0:09:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.72,0:09:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.52,0:09:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The show is ending soon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.16,0:10:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,When are you coming back to Korea?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm planning on going back sometime next week, after I'm done sorting some things out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Do you miss me that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.23,0:10:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's just that I..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.24,0:10:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.81,0:10:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something I really need to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.88,0:10:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll call you right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.41,0:10:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.38,0:10:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.76,0:10:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.87,0:10:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, what to do. Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.77,0:10:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.65,0:10:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.25,0:11:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you being like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.52,0:11:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I was trying to clean up after showering.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.83,0:11:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The maid cleans the bathroom and everything afterwards;
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.33,0:11:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't need to worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.43,0:11:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But I still... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.40,0:11:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.08,0:11:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Dry yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.38,0:11:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm okay..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.15,0:11:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.05,0:11:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.79,0:11:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You can catch a cold, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.53,0:11:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.00,0:11:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.57,0:11:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.97,0:11:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? I thought you were talking to your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:12:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.41,0:12:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.51,0:12:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He's never hung up on me first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.23,0:12:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make it quick. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.54,0:12:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's okay. Take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.87,0:12:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you fully dry yourself, so that you don't catch a cold. {\b1}- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.95,0:12:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.32,0:12:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I really want to thank you for earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.69,0:12:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.99,0:12:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. Go ahead and dry yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.37,0:13:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,♬ {\i1}From the day that you arrived,{\i} ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.97,0:13:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,♬ {\i1}I had no idea you'd be my life.{\i} ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.31,0:13:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,♬ {\i1}But when I looked into your eyes, I knew someday,{\i} ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,♬ {\i1}You'd be my wife.{\i} ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.89,0:13:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,♬ {\i1}I know there's times when I am wrong.{\i} ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.00,0:13:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,♬ {\i1}Just as long as we both give it all we can.{\i} ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.07,0:13:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,♬ {\i1}And for both to see that we try{\i} ♬ {\b1\i1}With you, Father,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.24,0:13:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I really have no secrets.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.57,0:13:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But that really makes me feel at ease.{\i\b1}♬ {\i1}You took my heart so unexpectedly{\i} ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.44,0:13:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm weird, aren't I?{\b1}♬ You took my heart so unexpectedly ♬{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe it's because you're a Father.{\i\b1}♬ {\i1}Who knew that you would{\i} ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.22,0:13:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,♬ {\i1}be the one.{\i} ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.85,0:14:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I doing? I feel like I'm conning her.{\b1}♬ {\i1}But I always knew that there was something special 'bout you{\i} ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.13,0:14:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,♬ {\i1}From the day that you walked into my life{\i} ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.13,0:14:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.77,0:14:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes, this is he. I am Daniel Pitt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.47,0:14:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You know very well that I don't attend those types of things. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.51,0:14:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.72,0:14:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make an exception this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.95,0:14:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make it low-key and quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.64,0:14:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it pretty? Yes, so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.78,0:14:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, today, it's the first set of clothes that our newborn baby will wear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.11,0:15:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be making clothes for the newborn infants.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.12,0:15:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it sound fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.98,0:15:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.85,0:15:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.39,0:15:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, the fathers will do the sewing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.46,0:15:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The fathers need to put their hearts and sincerity into each stitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.70,0:15:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, fathers, let's raise our needles.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.83,0:15:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, no need to be shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.60,0:15:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's how you do it. Start slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.37,0:15:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's good. Carefully, carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.44,0:15:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Help us over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.98,0:15:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.49,0:15:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.66,0:15:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Gun busy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.33,0:15:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be nice if he could be here to do this with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He's really busy with the company matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.17,0:15:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, he's probably never held a needle before, so he would've done a poor job.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.57,0:15:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I will make it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.97,0:16:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.61,0:16:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do a poor job?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.71,0:16:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor job...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.22,0:16:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.46,0:16:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.83,0:16:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it more important that I came?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.43,0:16:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.83,0:16:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean "poor job"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.74,0:16:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was in the military, my specialty was the overlock stitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I was an ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.81,0:16:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he was an ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.71,0:16:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I look forward to seeing your skills, Father Overlock.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.71,0:16:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.09,0:16:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you wouldn't come. If you're busy, you can leave. I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.23,0:16:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You said our baby would like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.06,0:17:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't upset the baby even while it's in your stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.80,0:17:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Our baby will sulk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.40,0:17:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand over the needle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.17,0:17:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thread.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.34,0:17:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.52,0:17:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,♬ {\i1}Oh, baby, I love you. Yes I do, like a lie{\i} ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.75,0:17:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,♬ {\i1}I cry and smile because of you.{\i} ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.39,0:17:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,♬ {\i1}I just wanna be with you, can you hear my heart?{\i} ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.06,0:17:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,♬ {\i1}Your love shines within all pain.{\i} ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.27,0:17:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You put it over like this, then
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.97,0:17:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,pull it like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.31,0:17:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the vertical line.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.64,0:17:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wipe my sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.55,0:17:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,One more time, one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.82,0:17:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we pull it straight up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.95,0:18:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.20,0:18:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this "Behind the White Tower" situation? {\i1\b1}*Famous medical drama{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.50,0:18:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, awesome. You're really good at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.17,0:18:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,♬ {\i1}Oh, baby, I'm so in love with you. Even more than yesterday,{\i} ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.41,0:18:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,♬ {\i1}my love grows every day.{\i} ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.15,0:18:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,♬ {\i1}Tell me that you love me. Your eyes{\i} ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.89,0:18:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, from here on it's really difficult. Look closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.16,0:18:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.34,0:18:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.44,0:18:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Are you hungry again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.64,0:18:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I want to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.74,0:18:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll cherish this and dress the baby with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.68,0:19:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why dress the baby with something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.75,0:19:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If you go to the department store, there are so many brand name baby clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.55,0:19:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But still. This is a one-of-a-kind baby clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.36,0:19:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If you cherish the clothes
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.99,0:19:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,that the baby wears for the first time, later when they take tests or
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.53,0:19:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,have some hardship, the baby will receive luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.47,0:19:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all a lie. A superstition, superstition. What era is it for you to still believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.95,0:19:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But still. I will cherish it forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.79,0:19:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, Gun oppa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.66,0:19:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oppa, you really don't remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.63,0:19:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this? I'm Se Ra's friend, Soo Hyun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.37,0:19:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.90,0:20:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Se... uh, Soo Hyun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.27,0:20:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I remember, I remember... Soo Hyun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.04,0:20:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But what business do you have here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.28,0:20:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Prenatal Care{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.55,0:20:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys came together?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.19,0:20:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... that... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.76,0:20:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Our factory decided to fund projects related to kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.73,0:20:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So we are on our way from the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.90,0:20:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,President, I will organize the things that we are interviewing today...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and inform you by tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.78,0:20:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I will go in first. I'll see you at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.41,0:20:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay. You worked hard. See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.92,0:20:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.56,0:20:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.33,0:21:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.38,0:21:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you throw this away?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.88,0:21:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.21,0:21:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking for a trashcan is harder than looking for treasure nowadays.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.58,0:21:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You are so nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.19,0:21:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Your secretary is really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.16,0:21:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. She should throw that away herself. Does she not have arms or legs?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.53,0:21:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say, Oppa?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.00,0:21:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, nothing. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.71,0:21:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.58,0:21:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oppa, did you see Se Ra's performance?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.78,0:21:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes? {\b1}- I didn't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.05,0:21:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,All the business seats were sold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.08,0:22:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't take economy seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.99,0:22:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get airplane tickets?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.86,0:22:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't ride buses.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.86,0:22:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Timing and Subtitles brought to you by The Fated Team @ Viki{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.44,0:23:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My Mom{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.55,0:23:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.85,0:23:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wench, did you not eat yet? Why do you sound so weak?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.52,0:23:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I be weak? Your ears are just weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.13,0:23:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go to Seoul because my friend's daughter is having a wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.70,0:23:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have time? Come with Son-in-law Lee.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.50,0:23:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see your faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.44,0:23:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.84,0:23:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I will ask Gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.21,0:23:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going back home right after the wedding,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.58,0:23:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,so take him and meet me there so that I can see him. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.41,0:23:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.08,0:23:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll see you tomorrow. {\b1}- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.19,0:23:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ji Yun{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.34,0:24:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How can they fire me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.08,0:24:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And with a phone call, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.18,0:24:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They didn't want to have a contract with me. No more!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.85,0:24:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why wouldn't they re-contract with you? You are good at working.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.79,0:24:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.86,0:24:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just going to drink. The Earth will spin only if I drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.03,0:24:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to live in a world with no bias.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.87,0:24:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ji Yun, stop drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.68,0:24:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you are not in this house, it feels so empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.32,0:24:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.49,0:24:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It was really nice when we lived together.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.63,0:25:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Unni, you wouldn't know because you are having such a good time with your husband, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.97,0:25:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Aigoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.18,0:25:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Unni.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.15,0:25:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Unni, you have to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.22,0:25:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You really have to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.72,0:25:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,My Unni!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.63,0:25:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're happy, then I'm fine. I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.00,0:25:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Ji Yun.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.40,0:25:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I should be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.74,0:25:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I should.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.07,0:25:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,My Unni! My Unni!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.48,0:25:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Unni is stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.08,0:25:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.82,0:26:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The world is stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.89,0:26:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,S-T-U-P-I-D.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.70,0:26:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My head...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.32,0:26:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the chip that made you a goddess of luck.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.83,0:26:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Take it.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.50,0:26:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I expect?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.12,0:27:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why isn't she answering her phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.69,0:27:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Did she go somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.03,0:28:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,♬ {\i1}When the twinkling stars{\i}♬
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.54,0:28:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,♬ {\i1}color in the dark night sky{\i} ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.07,0:28:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,♬ {\i1}I draw out the one star in my heart.{\i}♬
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.55,0:28:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,♬ {\i1}The hidden you{\i}♬
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.59,0:28:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,♬ {\i1}I don’t know why{\i} ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.12,0:29:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,♬ {\i1}The more I erase you with tears{\i} ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.06,0:29:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,♬ {\i1}The clearer you get{\i} ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.67,0:29:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,♬ {\i1}Don’t go away{\i} ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.00,0:29:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,♬ {\i1}When the long night passes and sun shines{\i} ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.91,0:29:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,♬ {\i1}I hope my warmth from my fingertips reaches you{\i} ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.48,0:29:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,♬ {\i1}My everything, my destiny{\i} ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.19,0:29:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,♬ {\i1}My heart keeps going to you{\i} ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.56,0:29:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,♬ {\i1}When I open my eyes, let me hear it{\i} ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.23,0:29:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♬ {\i1}Let me hear you saying I love you{\i} ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.50,0:29:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,♬ {\i1}Sweet melody{\i} ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.01,0:31:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the time, and she still hasn't woken up.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.91,0:31:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be right out ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.82,0:31:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,With that innocent face, as if she knows everything in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.79,0:31:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The daughter-in-laws in my time wouldn't even dream of being like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.13,0:31:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahjumma, give us a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.04,0:31:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have something to say,{\b1}I hope you call her and say it to her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.71,0:31:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I say wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.11,0:31:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Did your mom talk so badly about me to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.29,0:31:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess you wouldn't remember because you're mom passed away when you were in elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.20,0:31:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.77,0:32:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I only ever saw her back,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.74,0:32:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,because she didn't want me to see her cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.31,0:32:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see you at the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.85,0:32:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Please have a fun trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.26,0:32:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened? Did he bully you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.06,0:32:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.76,0:32:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That young jerk says anything he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.60,0:32:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I ever live while smiling?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.70,0:32:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I have dry eyes because there aren't any tears left to spill.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.91,0:32:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Son, I think I'll die from stress before the elders if I continue living like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.45,0:32:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't happen, Mom! Then from whom will I live off of...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.72,0:32:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, wait a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.59,0:32:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If my instincts are right,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.79,0:33:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,something smells weird at the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.23,0:33:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna make him bleed.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.24,0:33:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But... why am I - am I still sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.29,0:34:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[July 23 - Day Mom's coming over]{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.71,0:34:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to get timely examinations even when you're busy. Why don't you ever listen?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.28,0:34:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I was busy all this time. I'm here already.{\b1}Why keep nagging?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.68,0:34:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.35,0:34:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you see something?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.85,0:34:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something? What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.29,0:34:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the black thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.06,0:34:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.13,0:34:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that something bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.86,0:34:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing wrong. It's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.10,0:34:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Your levels are normal, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.47,0:34:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! You gave me a scare, Dr. Octopus!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.00,0:35:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever the case, all you have to do is carefully overcome your obstacles.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.04,0:35:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If it attacks, it could be fatal.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.18,0:35:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But since it didn't attack your father either, don't worry too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.75,0:35:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Telling me to worry and then not to.{\b1}This is not a matter of money!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.98,0:35:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Say it clearly. What do you want me to do? What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.79,0:35:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Fix your temper first!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.92,0:35:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If your mind rots, your body will rot, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.09,0:35:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, this old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.50,0:35:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Nag, nag, nag. I'm gonna die from stress because of your nagging.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.20,0:35:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to die while yelling in anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.40,0:35:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think genetic diseases are scary for no reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.00,0:35:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you to be careful because it may suddenly appear anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.97,0:35:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand, I got it. Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.61,0:35:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, that's a relief (that nothing's wrong).
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.18,0:35:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.39,0:35:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.06,0:35:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.30,0:36:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How am I going to tell mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.94,0:36:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, what am I going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.91,0:36:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Mi Young!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.74,0:36:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you coming now?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.68,0:36:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.{\b1}- Hurry, let's go inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.34,0:36:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.48,0:36:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Cha cha-ri cha-ri cha-ri cha cha cha ♪{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.62,0:36:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ When you need me, just call me over ♪{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.92,0:36:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ I'll run to you anytime ♪{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.92,0:36:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.36,0:36:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and go!{\b1\i1}♪ Whether day or night ♪{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.89,0:36:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ I'll run to you anytime ♪{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.10,0:36:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ If other people ask ♪{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.27,0:36:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ I'll think about it for a while ♪{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.64,0:36:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ If you call for me ♪{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.37,0:36:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ I will run to you no matter what ♪{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.74,0:36:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Cha cha-ri cha-ri cha-ri cha cha cha ♪{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.91,0:36:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ The love that I have for you ♪{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.02,0:36:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Is a love like no other ♪{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.05,0:37:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Even if I have to cross the Pacific Ocean, the Indian Ocean, or Yeoul Island ♪{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.56,0:37:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.43,0:37:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ If you call, I'll run to you ♪{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.60,0:37:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ I'll run to you no matter what ♪{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.03,0:37:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Cha cha-ri cha-ri cha-ri cha cha cha ♪{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.91,0:37:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There, there, his wife came.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.18,0:37:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The wife is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.05,0:37:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Aigo, you girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.48,0:37:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Son-in-law already came, and you weren't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.58,0:37:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you arrive now?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.65,0:37:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.49,0:37:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you purposely not tell me so that you could see me get slapped again?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.86,0:37:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.33,0:37:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that it'd be a burden to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.29,0:37:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, don't be like that and sing a song together. Let's hear a newlywed couple's song.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.20,0:37:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah! Let's hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.97,0:37:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.14,0:37:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to do it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.84,0:37:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother-in-law, I request number 1064.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.81,0:37:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Chuli and Miae - Why do you]{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.94,0:37:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Oh Uh Woo woo ♪{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.85,0:38:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, I will begin now!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.56,0:38:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ I am very angry now and can't hold it in anymore ♪{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.33,0:38:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ You who loved me is now seeing another man ♪{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.10,0:38:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ My god, now I'm walking towards you ♪{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.90,0:38:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ You must be looking and worrying about this and that ♪{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.11,0:38:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Don't misunderstand ♪{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.51,0:38:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Tell me who is that man ♪{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.75,0:38:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ That's not true ♪{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.31,0:38:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Then tell me the truth ♪{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.42,0:38:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ I only love you ♪{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.02,0:38:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Instead tell me if you want to leave me ♪{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.99,0:38:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Oh~ Why do you ♪{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.89,0:38:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Oh oh oh~ ♪{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.79,0:38:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Why do you still not know ♪{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.39,0:38:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ My only love for you ♪{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.20,0:38:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Why do you still not know ♪{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.90,0:38:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ All I have left is my love for you ♪{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.85,0:39:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Even if she's really, really pretty ♪{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.45,0:39:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ I would always reject her for I thought of you ♪{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.72,0:39:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ But this is the only time, I swear ♪{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.73,0:39:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ I set up a date and I arrived on that day ♪{\i\b1\i1}♪ I dressed up specially and even did my hair ♪{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.23,0:39:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ I wondered what I would say on the blind date ♪{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.40,0:39:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You really have a great son-in-law.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.21,0:39:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought he'd be an ass because he's from a wealthy family.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.61,0:39:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Mi Young must have saved the world in her previous life.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.21,0:39:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Aigoo, that's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.98,0:39:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,When I first saw our son-in-law Lee,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.75,0:39:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I already knew he would be the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.09,0:39:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.09,0:40:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Forgive me just this once ♪{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.10,0:40:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Aigoo, you are so handsome. {\b1} -Have a safe trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.07,0:40:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You are so lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.34,0:40:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, run, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.07,0:40:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You are so handsome... Aigoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.44,0:40:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Run! Cross the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.18,0:40:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Cross the Pacific!{\b1}-How handsome!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.91,0:40:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Today was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.55,0:40:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Go already!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.02,0:40:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to cross the Pacific and the Atlantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.05,0:40:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.12,0:40:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Aigoo, Son-in-law Lee, you worked hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.33,0:40:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's tiring to amuse those country women, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.56,0:40:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It was nothing hard, it was okay actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.03,0:40:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really thankful.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.14,0:40:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were not treating Mi Young well, so honestly
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.30,0:40:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a bit suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.97,0:40:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.98,0:40:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's a mother's heart. A mother's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.51,0:40:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Think of me as your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.45,0:41:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,How lonely it must have been without your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.25,0:41:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, I am your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.62,0:41:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother? {\b1}-That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.89,0:41:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Mi Young, you really have to treat your husband well, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.90,0:41:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.03,0:41:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Aigoo, but you seem thinner than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.54,0:41:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask Mi Young to make you some delicious food.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.31,0:41:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,My son has to be well, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.31,0:41:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. Mom's is leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.55,0:41:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Aigoo. Aigoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.45,0:41:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom. {\b1}-Yes, my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.19,0:41:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.26,0:41:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.60,0:41:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom! {\b1}- Huh?!Have a safe trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.33,0:41:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to have a safe trip! {\b1} - Of course, of course~
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.30,0:41:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.14,0:41:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.74,0:41:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.91,0:41:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.98,0:42:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's go! Cross the Pacific!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.02,0:42:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Run! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.89,0:42:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.49,0:42:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Timing and Subtitles brought to you by The Fated Team @ Viki{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.84,0:42:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really thankful. I couldn't even imagine it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.08,0:42:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know the saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.05,0:42:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A son-in-law is also a son.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.45,0:42:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But you, you were better at singing than you looked like you'd be.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.75,0:42:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You could be a singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.49,0:42:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Your rap was amazing, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.33,0:42:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You were like Eminem.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.16,0:42:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to do something like that before. A project.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.60,0:42:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you eaten?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.44,0:43:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.38,0:43:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief Tak, what happened to that thing I asked you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.82,0:43:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,CEO.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.49,0:43:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.12,0:43:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,At Yeoul Island,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.12,0:43:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,they're making an industrial waste landfill.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.73,0:43:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They are making what? That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.73,0:43:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} This is Lawyer Hong. {\i} That DuDu Industries
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.23,0:43:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,is gathering electronic waste and industrial waste
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.97,0:43:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and burying it in mountains and dumping it into the sea. The've been sued
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.57,0:43:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,multiple times already.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.24,0:43:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This- {\b1} -What are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.47,0:43:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When your wife finds out, she will be very upset.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.71,0:43:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She would be very upset!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.65,0:43:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,AH! You scared me!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.32,0:43:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You scared me!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.65,0:43:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Why were so surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.12,0:43:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You came out of nowhere, who wouldn't be scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.96,0:43:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I scared you. {\b1\i1} -CEO, why aren't you saying anything?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.32,0:43:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I will quickly-
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.13,0:43:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Kim Mi Young! {\b1\i1} -CEO!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.43,0:44:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Your phone... {\b1} -Kim Mi Young!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.83,0:44:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...are...you...to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.71,0:44:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean why?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.51,0:44:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}HEY, CEO!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.35,0:44:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why were you still walking around and not going to sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.18,0:44:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my place so I was going to sleep, but I'll come back later.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.82,0:44:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, you're place. No, I should go. That's right. I should leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.46,0:44:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But you, why did you hug me from the back all the sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.29,0:44:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.74,0:44:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But you were the one hugging me...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.15,0:44:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Just exactly what did you do? Am I crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.36,0:45:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The flight is still days later. Why are you packing up now?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.56,0:45:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you that excited?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.86,0:45:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.24,0:45:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.04,0:45:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I have done a lot of bad things so I have to make up for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.91,0:45:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Cuff links. Aren't they pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.68,0:45:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If Gun wears these and signs a contract, he'll look really cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.59,0:45:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay for you not to call? Wouldn't it be too surprising?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.49,0:45:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't sound too well when I talked to him on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.90,0:45:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The company must not be doing so great.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.37,0:45:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to interfere with his work.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.97,0:45:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,When I see his face...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.84,0:45:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll him hug tightly,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.91,0:45:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and tell him all the things I wasn't able to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.75,0:46:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,CEO, you need to be there an hour before.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.72,0:46:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as you expected, the exhibition is today.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.65,0:46:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I can just take care of it over there. Keep alert while we're there.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.16,0:46:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.63,0:46:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,CEO, I have something to report to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.83,0:46:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You rude thing. Don't you see me leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.23,0:46:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,See me later.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.37,0:46:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.24,0:46:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's very hot! Take care of your skin so it won't get burned!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.71,0:46:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a good time!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.48,0:46:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it got all wrinkled.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.15,0:46:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are they going so quickly?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.62,0:46:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.05,0:46:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really know, but
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.62,0:46:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I know they're going to DuDu Industries to discuss the Yeoul Island issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.09,0:46:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,DuDu Industries... Yeoul Island?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.57,0:47:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom! Mom! Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.80,0:47:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What is so urgent that you called me up?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.51,0:47:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Surprise! Watch carefully. You will surely love this.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.32,0:47:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Jangin Chemicals Yeoul Island Purchase.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.79,0:47:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeoul Island? Isn't that Gun's wife's hometown? {\b1} -Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.66,0:47:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That woman's hometown.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.83,0:47:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Gun sold it to DuDu Industries.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.70,0:47:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So? If it's worth money, you should sell it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.10,0:47:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't fun if it just ended there.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.84,0:47:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what DuDu Industries is going to build there?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.21,0:47:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The guys who line up behind me at work say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.38,0:47:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my. What in the world. He sold it even though he knew they'd build something like that in his wife's hometown?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.32,0:47:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly. If that woman finds out, what do you think will happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.02,0:47:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean. Those two, will be the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.39,0:48:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,End!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.77,0:48:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It says it's made out to you, but the sender isn't written.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.84,0:48:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.07,0:48:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,To Kim Mi Young.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.12,0:48:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mi Young, you know I've always been sincere with you, right?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.88,0:48:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have something to say. Let's meet up at this place at 1 o'clock.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.35,0:48:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will wait until you come.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.62,0:48:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.93,0:48:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♬ Those days without you, how lonely they were ♬{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.97,0:48:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♬ You who is far away, thoughts of you grow long today ♬{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.91,0:48:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♬ When I miss you're white face, I draw you in my mind ♬{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.95,0:49:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♬ The day we can meet again, I counted the days with my fingers ♬{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.99,0:49:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You! How many times have I told you not to just come in and out when you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.36,0:49:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,YOU! Act properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.14,0:49:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.92,0:49:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This Yeoul Island Purchase Agreement,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.39,0:49:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm cancelling it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.69,0:49:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think this contract is a joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.70,0:49:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think of me as a joke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.24,0:49:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.44,0:50:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, since this issue is due to my change of heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.14,0:50:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be sure to give you an unimaginable amount of compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.01,0:50:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Look here, Lee Gun CEO!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.92,0:50:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the one who wanted to sell the factory quickly...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.79,0:50:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the reason you are suddenly paying the breach of contract fee?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.83,0:50:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You should know.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.90,0:50:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That island,...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.93,0:50:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,is not a lousy and worthless island that
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.30,0:50:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,you can use for your dirty industrial wasteland.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.11,0:50:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Our Yeoul Island's seas{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.71,0:50:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} are one of the cleanest seas in our nation{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.95,0:50:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} and the air is very good.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.39,0:50:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} It's small but it's a beautiful place.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.56,0:50:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} So, to me,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.26,0:50:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} I feel proud to have Yeoul Island as my hometown.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.57,0:51:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Lee CEO,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.51,0:51:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,how much will it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.81,0:51:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If money is the problem, I swear I'll go beyond my limits and
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.95,0:51:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pay you anything! Now, tell me any amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.11,0:51:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Look here, CEO Cha.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.37,0:51:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If I say I won't be selling once, that means I will never be selling it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.01,0:51:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, that island, is my wife's hometown.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.05,0:51:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I die,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.35,0:51:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,my decision
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.82,0:52:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,will never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.46,0:52:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.75,0:52:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[D. Pitt - Exhibition]{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.09,0:52:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an honor to be able to exhibit the artist's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.02,0:52:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here is Exhibit No. 1
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.93,0:52:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and Exhibit No. 2 is over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.53,0:52:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me. Just do your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.93,0:52:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I will just quietly look.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.00,0:52:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
