Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.41,0:54:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hundreds, thousands, millions...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.68,0:54:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ I miss you ♪{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.21,0:54:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ I clearly see you ♪{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.92,0:54:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ In that place ♪{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.59,0:54:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ talking alone ♪{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.36,0:54:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ I give you my hand ♪{\i}
