Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.27,0:55:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ even tangled fate can become love ♪{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.61,0:55:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ I yell ♪{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.91,0:55:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ I yell ♪{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.85,0:55:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ that I only love you ♪{\i}
