Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.62,0:55:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,♬ {\i1} You who's like my destiny {\i} ♬
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.51,0:55:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Jangin Chemicals and DuDu Industries Purchase of Yeoul Island{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.01,0:55:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Jangin Chemicals and DuDu Industries Purchase of Yeoul Island{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.75,0:55:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Jangin Chemicals and DuDu Industries Purchase of Yeoul Island{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.99,0:56:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mi Young.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.63,0:56:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.40,0:56:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.77,0:56:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.57,0:56:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.44,0:56:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,To me, I thought that...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.58,0:56:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,that person was a really good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.82,0:56:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He could've ignored me and my baby,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.96,0:56:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,but he didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.33,0:56:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And he did all he can do for my hometown people.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.00,0:56:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And so,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.17,0:56:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,perhaps,... perhaps,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.77,0:56:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,more than me,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.47,0:56:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,he could be more important to the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.18,0:56:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.52,0:57:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,now,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.05,0:57:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know who that person is anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.72,0:57:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.50,0:57:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha-
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.82,0:57:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.43,0:57:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I'll be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.57,0:58:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we check what kind of person he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.29,0:58:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,♬ {\i1}Oh baby, I love you, yes I do {\i}♬
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.36,0:58:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,♬ {\i1}Like a lie, I {\i}♬
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.46,0:58:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,♬ {\i1} I cry and cry because of you {\i}♬
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.06,0:58:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ I just wanna be with you ♪{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.70,0:58:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Can you hear my heart? ♪{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.77,0:58:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}~Preview~{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.10,0:58:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} I can't go to that person.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.34,0:58:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You have to speak for me to know. Now why are you doing this?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.18,0:58:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You are avoiding him{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.01,0:58:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}because it's hard, right?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.25,0:58:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} I'm FREE! {\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.02,0:58:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What are you doing...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.99,0:58:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to another man's wife?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.39,0:58:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you sure that she is your woman?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.92,0:58:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Give up!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.73,0:58:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} The word 'give up' doesn't exist in my dictionary. {\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.79,0:59:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} What's the real reason why you want to work with our company?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.50,0:59:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Is it because of my wife?{\i}
